text: Mariam Sabine Salloum (born 23 August 1989) is a German water polo player. She played for the German women's national water polo team in the 2009 World Aquatics Championships. She played for Arizona State University's women's water polo team. == References == ==Other websites== * salloum-of-germany- fights-for-a-ball-with-cabout-of-netherlands stock.adobe.com category:1989 births Category:Living people category:German water polo players
